\begin_layout Subsection*

\lang english
1.
 Purpose
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
This policy establishes physical and environmental safeguards for Elko County facilities,
 information systems,
 and Criminal Justice Information (CJI).
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection*

\lang english
2.
 Scope
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
This policy applies to all Elko County physical facilities,
 data centers,
 network closets,
 and terminal areas where County information systems reside or where Criminal Justice Information (CJI) is accessed,
 processed,
 transmitted,
 or stored,
 and to all Information Operations personnel,
 Buildings and Grounds personnel,
 and all County Personnel who access or work within those locations.
\end_layout

