\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Perimeter physical access controls,
 signage,
 and structural separation of secure locations from non-secure locations.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Physical access authorization,
 visitor escort,
 and visitor record-keeping.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Physical access audit logs and security camera surveillance systems protecting County information assets.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Environmental controls including fire protection,
 temperature and humidity regulation,
 and water damage protection.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Power equipment,
 emergency shutoff,
 emergency lighting,
 and uninterruptible power supply (UPS) serving critical information technology infrastructure.
